          </p>
          <p>
            The current  Acting Administrator of SRA is David John Thaddeus P. Alba concurrently sits in the Sugar Board with board members , Pablo Luis S. Azcona representing the planters’ sector and Ma. Mitzi V. Mangwag, representing the millers’ sector, under the chairmanship of the Department of Agriculture Secretary, President FERDINAND “Bongbong” R. MARCOS, Jr.
          </p>
          <p>
            A chronology of laws and statutes which charted the significant events of the sugar industry is presented here under.
          </p>
          <p>
            The Philippine sugar industry has sailed through rough and better times. During adverse circumstances, the industry has always been victorious. In these critical times, one note of optimism pervading the industry is that "when one reaches the bottom, there is no other way but up".
          </p>
